millsfield:images_texts:
Food and drinks are served right after takeoff, but if you'd like to be
served later, no problem. Just ask your in-flight team.
BREAKFAST
ENTREES
Breakfast is served with a flaky buttery croissant.
Contains wheat, dairy, and sugar
MUSHROOM SPINACH OMELET
Cage-free eggs and chives, spinach, sautéed
mushrooms, gruyere and mozzarella cheeses topped
with creme fraiche. Herb roasted Yukon gold potatoes,
tomato, and chicken sundried tomato sausage.
Contains egg, dairy, and optional poultry
CHERRY ALMOND PORRIDGE
Savory porridge of farro, quinoa, millet, and oats all
simmered in lowfat and coconut milk. Served hot with
cinnamon, sides of Greek yogurt, brown sugar, and a
mix of dried cherries, golden raisins and almonds.
Contains dairy, optional nuts and sugar
Hot entrees are served with a fruit salad of mango,
pineapple, orange, kiwi, pomegranate seeds, and
orange-cardamom syrup.
contains sucan
GNOCCHI RICOTTA GORGONZOLA
Potato gnocchi stuffed with ricotta and blue cheese.
Topped with a truffle butter sauce, sautéed wild
mushrooms, roasted delicata squash and chopped
fines herbs.
Contains wheat, egg, and dairy
DESSERT
FLOURLESS CHOCOLATE CAKE
Contains egg, sugar, and dairy
SNACKS ANYTIME
TOP SHELF BITES
Nibble on a spread of delectable Dean & Deluca snacks
throughout the flight.
Our apologies if your first choice is unavailable.
Rest assured, your second choice will be just as delicious.
LUNCH & DINNER
APPETIZER
Flights over four hours
TUSCAN KALE SALAD
Tuscan kale and baby arugula, sliced radishes, fresh
persimmon, ricotta salata cheese, and a Dijon-sherry
vinaigrette.
Contains optional dairy and sugar
Flights four hours and under
SIMPLE SALAD
Mesclun mix with chives, chervil, basil leaves, and
cherry tomatoes. Served with an olive oil-balsamic
vinaigrette.
Lunch and Dinner are served with a Multigrain Roll
Contains wheat
ENTRÉES
FILET MIGNON
Grilled filet of beef, red chard braised with bacon,
balsamic marinated cippolini onions, herb roasted
yukon gold potatoes, and a red chimichurri sauce.
Contains beef, pork, and dairy
plenty of both!
